    • Method Detail

      • determineScoreOrder

        public int[][] determineScoreOrder(HomeHealthRecordIF record)
        Returns a non-null double array of int[6][3]. The values in the array elements are as follows:
        • 0 - not scored
        • 1 - score during first round
        • 2 - score during second round
        Stand alone etiology codes are always scored first, then the manifestation/ etiology pair codes are scored second. Codes that are not valid for scoring are not evaluated and there for entry in the array will be 0
        Overrides:
        determineScoreOrder in class AbstractGrouper
